{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ensure GCSE students are issued equation sheets in 2024",
        "additional_details": "We want the Government to do this because we think that Covid-19 had an impact on everyone's learning and that having to learn all the equations puts too much pressure on students.",
        "background": "We want the Government to ensure current Years 10s are given the form of formulae and equations sheets for GCSE mathematics, physics and combined science in 2024. This has been arranged for 2023, and we want it to also apply to current Year 10s.",
